[normal]ff
[normal]ort
[normal]s
[normal].
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]The report also identified substantial evidence that crime statistics were not being recorded in a consistent way. As a consequence and 
[normal]in an 
[normal]attempt to r
[normal]emove 
[normal]a
[normal]m
[normal]b
[normal]i
