[normal]y 
[normal]a
[normal]nd provide clarity for Forces,
[normal] ACPO and the Home Office developed the National Crime Recording Standard (NCRS). The 
[normal]NCRS was introduced nationally on 1 April 2002 and was aimed at promoting greater consistency between police forces in the recording of crime and at taking a more victim oriented approach. It 
[normal]included comprehensive
[normal] g
[normal]u
[normal]i
[normal]d
[normal]a
